title: Book My Book
description: A full-stack book reservation application using Spring Boot, React.js, and MySQL. Users can search, reserve, and manage books.

title: Car Rental System
description: A full-stack car rental platform built with Spring Boot, React.js, and MySQL. It offers car booking, rental management, and secure payment processing.
